				%li <a href=http://tdg.me/about>Tom de Grunwald</a> is a producer and strategist working in London and Cambridge. With a background in social media and broadcast projects (Unreported World, Downton Abbey, Radio 1Xtra); he also helped bring together the UK digital community in a <a href="http://bit.ly/dbuc">series of unconferences</a> to debate and influence the 2010 Digital Economy Act, <a href="http://blog.swapmyvote.uk/post/116080891268/how-a-blog-post-became-a-platform-for-change">proposing Swap my Vote in a blog post</a> that year. 






